  <brief_title>Body-fluid Balance and Drinking Habits in Patients With Retinal Vascular Occlusion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Examination of the Body-fluid Balance in Patients With Retinal Vascular Occlusion Before and During Hemodilution and the Influence of Drinking Habits on the Degree of Body Hydration</official_title>
  <sponsors>
